msgid "## 1. 函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/minimum.md:4
msgid "简介：计算x和y的逐元素最小值。"
msgstr "Introduction: Compute the element-wise minimum of x and y."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/minimum.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.minimum(x, y, propagate_nan: ~triton.language.core.constexpr = <PROPAGATE_NAN.NONE: 0>, _semantic=None)¶\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/minimum.md:8
msgid "## 2. 规格"
msgstr "## 2. Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/minimum.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/minimum.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                | 说明                                                             |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `x`        | `tensor`          | 张量数据                                                      |\n"
"| `y`       | `tensor`    | 张量数据                                                        |\n"
"| `propagate_nan`       | `tl.PropagateNan`    | 是否传播NaN值                                                        |\n"
"| `_semantic`   | -                 | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Description |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `x`        | `tensor`          | Tensor data                                                      |\n"
"| `y`       | `tensor`    | Tensor data                                                        |\n"
"| `propagate_nan`       | `tl.PropagateNan`    | Whether to propagate NaN values                                                        |\n"
"| `_semantic`   | -                 | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported temporarily |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/minimum.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`x`：与输入x的shape相同的张量\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`x`: A tensor with the same shape as the input `x`.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/minimum.md:16
msgid "### 2.2 OP 规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/minimum.md:18
